---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import hero from "@/assets/agricultura/hero-colza.jpg";

const notes = [
  "Cultivos cerealistas y forrajeros",
  "Trabajo ligado a la campana",
  "Conexion directa con la ganaderia",
];
---

<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden border-b border-stone-200 bg-stone-100 text-stone-950">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <Image
      src={hero}
      alt="Cultivos de Iturribero Abereak en Durana, Alava"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
      sizes="100vw"
      loading="eager"
      priority
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,_rgba(245,245,244,0.74)_0%,_rgba(245,245,244,0.56)_34%,_rgba(245,245,244,0.08)_64%,_rgba(28,25,23,0.24)_100%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,_rgba(245,158,11,0.08),_transparent_30%)]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto flex min-h-[58vh] max-w-7xl items-end px-6 py-14 md:min-h-[62vh] md:px-8 md:py-16">
    <div class="grid w-full gap-14 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.95fr)_minmax(0,1.05fr)] lg:items-end">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="eyebrow text-stone-500">
          Agricultura
        </p>

        <h1 class="mt-5 text-5xl font-semibold leading-[0.96] tracking-[-0.045em] text-stone-950 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          El campo marca
          <br />
          el calendario.
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-stone-600 md:text-lg">
          Cultivamos cereal y forraje en Durana, Alava, con decisiones que se
          toman segun suelo, clima, tiempo de trabajo y necesidades reales de la explotacion.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {notes.map((note) => (
            <span class="rounded-full border border-stone-300 bg-white/80 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-stone-700 shadow-[0_10px_24px_-18px_rgba(28,25,23,0.35)] backdrop-blur-sm">
              {note}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:justify-self-end lg:max-w-xl">
        <div class="grid gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-stone-300 bg-stone-300 shadow-[0_30px_80px_-56px_rgba(28,25,23,0.45)] md:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="bg-white/86 p-5 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-stone-500">
              Suelo
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-tight text-stone-950">
              Mantener la tierra en condiciones para la siguiente campana.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="bg-white/78 p-5 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-stone-500">
              Ritmo
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-tight text-stone-950">
              Sembrar, seguir y cosechar cuando el momento acompana.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="bg-stone-950 p-5 text-white">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-amber-200/90">
              Ganado
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">
              Parte del cultivo vuelve a la explotacion como alimento.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
